## Account Health Check Workflow

Conduct a comprehensive health review:

- [ ] 1. Revenue analysis: Review {{current_revenue}}, contract terms, and renewal timeline ({{renewal_date}})
- [ ] 2. Satisfaction signals: Check NPS/feedback scores, escalations, and complaint patterns
- [ ] 3. Engagement levels: Assess communication frequency, meeting attendance, and collaboration quality
- [ ] 4. Performance review: Compare actual vs expected KPIs for {{account_name}}
- [ ] 5. Competitive intel: Note any competitor activity or switching intent signals
- [ ] 6. Risk scoring: Calculate overall health score and identify red flags

## Account Details
- Account: {{account_name}}
- Industry: {{industry}}
- Current revenue: {{current_revenue}}
- Contract renewal: {{renewal_date}}
